{
  "texts": [
    "See Section 5.3.2 for discussion.",
    "Notes: On 10,000 Congressional bills, we prompt GPT-3.5-Turbo and GPT-4o to label each description for its policy topic area using alternative prompting strategies.",
    "For each model m and prompt p, we regress V m,p r on the linked covariate W r, where V m,p r are indicators for the policy topic of the bill (i.e., Health, Banking, Finance and Domestic Commerce, Defense, Government Operations and Public Lands and Water Management) and the covariates W r are whether the bill's sponsor was a Democrat, whether the bill originated in the Senate, and the DW1 score of the bill's sponsor.",
    "In each subplot, the t-score estimates were sorted in ascending order for clarity.",
    "See Section 5.3.3 for discussion."
  ]
}